AMEN 🙏🏿 #PassTheCROWN 

Repost from @naacp_ldf
•
Black hair belongs in the classroom. In court.  At the podium. In the workplace. Wherever it grows. 

#CROWNDay is July 3, and, we’re celebrating the iconic nature of Black hair. From cornrows, to locs, to afros, to durags, natural hair and protective styles should be able to be worn without fear and judgement. 

👑  Join us in fighting against race-based hair discrimination and help #PassTheCROWN by signing the CROWN Act petition at thecrownact.com
